OL,3,CTop Welsh GCSE results fall and still
OL,4,Clower than pre-pandemic levels
OL,6,F"Arrangements for qualifications this
OL,7,Fyear were the final stage of a gradual
OL,8,Freturn to pre-pandemic processes that
OL,9,Fcommenced when formal exams returned
OL,10,Fin 2022.
OL,12,F"Differences in approaches to awarding
OL,13,Fover the last four years mean that
OL,14,Fcomparisons should not be drawn
OL,15,Fbetween annual outcomes during this
OL,16,Fperiod."
