OL,3,CTop Welsh GCSE results fall and still
OL,4,Clower than pre-pandemic levels
OL,6,F"That's why it was important for us to
OL,7,Freturn to usual assessment
OL,8,Farrangements this year following the
OL,9,Fpandemic, to make sure there's long-
OL,10,Fterm fairness for all learners.
OL,12,FThe Welsh Conservatives Shadow
OL,13,FEducation Minister, Tom Giffard MS
OL,14,Fsaid, "It is worrying that unlike the
OL,15,FA-Level results last week, GCSE
OL,16,Fresults are down compared to pre
OL,17,Fpandemic figures. The Welsh Government
OL,18,Fmust come forward with a plan to
OL,19,Faddress this drop."
